From: Arnaud Rebillout <arnaudr@debian.org>
Date: Tue, 18 Nov 2025 15:21:00 +0700
Subject: [PATCH] Port xhydra to GTK 3

Some links of interest:
- https://www.manpagez.com/html/gtk2/gtk2-2.24.29/migrating-GtkCombo.php
- https://www.manpagez.com/html/gtk2/gtk2-2.24.29/gtk-migrating-tooltips.php
- https://docs.gtk.org/gtk3/migrating-2to3.html
---
 Dockerfile                |   2 +-
 INSTALL                   |   4 +-
 README                    |   2 +-
 configure                 |   6 +-
 hydra-gtk/README          |   2 +-
 hydra-gtk/configure       |   2 +-
 hydra-gtk/src/callbacks.c |   8 +-
 hydra-gtk/src/callbacks.h |   4 +-
 hydra-gtk/src/interface.c | 263 ++++++++++++++++++--------------------
 hydra-gtk/src/main.c      |   1 -
 hydra-gtk/src/support.c   |   4 +-
