 xhydra.1                  |   2 +-
 13 files changed, 148 insertions(+), 160 deletions(-)

diff --git a/Dockerfile b/Dockerfile
index 9f16b02a..aaeb8c87 100644
--- a/Dockerfile
+++ b/Dockerfile
@@ -22,7 +22,7 @@ RUN set -x \
         #libgcrypt11-dev \
         libgcrypt-dev \
         #libgcrypt20-dev \
-        #libgtk2.0-dev \
+        #libgtk-3-dev \
         libpcre3-dev \
         #firebird-dev \
         libidn11-dev \
diff --git a/INSTALL b/INSTALL
index 20f12fdf..5c0affd2 100644
--- a/INSTALL
+++ b/INSTALL
@@ -2,7 +2,7 @@ type "./configure", then "make" and finally "sudo make install"
 
 For special modules you need to install software packages before
 you run "./configure":
-  Ubuntu/Debian:  apt-get install libssl-dev libssh-dev libidn11-dev libpcre3-dev libgtk2.0-dev libmysqlclient-dev libpq-dev libsvn-dev firebird-dev libncurses5-dev
+  Ubuntu/Debian:  apt-get install libssl-dev libssh-dev libidn11-dev libpcre3-dev libgtk-3-dev libmysqlclient-dev libpq-dev libsvn-dev firebird-dev libncurses5-dev
   Redhat/Fedora:  yum install openssl-devel pcre-devel ncpfs-devel postgresql-devel libssh-devel subversion-devel libncurses-devel
   OpenSuSE:       zypper install libopenssl-devel pcre-devel libidn-devel ncpfs-devel libssh-devel postgresql-devel subversion-devel libncurses-devel
 
@@ -11,7 +11,7 @@ For Termux/Android you need the following setup:
 
 Install the necessary dependencies
   # pkg install -y x11-repo
-  # pkg install -y clang make openssl openssl-tool wget openssh coreutils gtk2 gtk3
+  # pkg install -y clang make openssl openssl-tool wget openssh coreutils gtk3
 And then compiling hydra
   # ./configure --prefix=$PREFIX
   # make
diff --git a/README b/README
index 6b7e4380..1fc930f1 100644
--- a/README
+++ b/README
@@ -94,7 +94,7 @@ for a few optional modules (note that some might not be available on your distri
 
 ```
 apt-get install libssl-dev libssh-dev libidn11-dev libpcre3-dev \
-                 libgtk2.0-dev libmysqlclient-dev libpq-dev libsvn-dev \
+                 libgtk-3-dev libmysqlclient-dev libpq-dev libsvn-dev \
                  firebird-dev libmemcached-dev libgpg-error-dev \
                  libgcrypt11-dev libgcrypt20-dev freetds-dev
 ```
